        "text_hh8DiB": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>It is said that flowers are nature’s gift to the world. And while that’s undeniably true, we’d amend that statement slightly. We believe that our handcrafted representations of the real thing take gift-giving to an even higher plateau. Because our high quality silk and artificial plants provide all the visual inspiration with none of the hassle of daily maintenance. Whether for home or office, our creations are designed and assembled in the USA, then expertly packaged and shipped, ready to display right out of the box. Gift giving has never been easier!</p>",
